correctness.rationale: Major schema violations and multiple factual/units errors. Key issues: (1) Numerous required numeric fields are set to null/None, which violates the schema: processParameters.pressure.quantityValue.numericValue, thicknessControl.filmThickness.quantityValue.numericValue, nucleationPeriod.quantityValue.numericValue, flowRates.*.quantityValue.numericValue, and many materialProperties and deviceProperties numeric fields; otherAspects.filmStability and reproducibility are booleans but set to None. (2) Dosing/purge times are wrong in units: article states 1.65 s (reactants) and 4.4 s (N2 purge); schema unit provided is MilliSEC, so values must be 1650 ms and 4400 ms, not 1.65 and 4.4. (3) Resistivity values are incorrectly reported in OHM-M without conversion: 0.53 Ω·cm (Film A) should be 0.0053 OHM-M; 14.7 Ω·cm (Film B) should be 0.147 OHM-M. (4) Unsubstantiated/incorrect entries: saturation set to True without support; filmComposition.atomicRatio set to 1:1 with XRD as method—article does not report atomic ratio and XRD is not appropriate for this; optical/device/uniformity/conformality/roughness/density values are not reported but included with nulls. (5) plasmaPower is included as None even though not PEALD—remove this field to comply. (6) filmThickness is required by the schema but left null; it can be computed from GPC and cycles (A: ~618 nm; B: ~414 nm) if reported/assumed linearity. (7) Pressure and flow rates are required but not provided; leaving them null violates the schema. (8) The article describes a third process (Process C: DEZ/N2/H2O/O2/N2 at 180 °C) that is not extracted—missing process. Corrective actions: remove invalid null fields or supply valid numeric values with correct QUDT units; fix dosing/purge times to 1650/4400 ms; convert resistivities to OHM-M; remove unsupported atomic ratio and saturation claims or provide evidence; compute and fill film thickness if appropriate; add the third process (Process C); omit optional subfields that are not reported to avoid schema violations.

completeness.rationale: Major omissions and multiple schema violations. (1) Missing processes: the article reports three ALD processes at 180 °C (A: DEZ/N2/H2O/N2; B: DEZ/N2/O2/H2O/N2; C: DEZ/N2/H2O/O2/N2) but only A and B are extracted. It also reports additional DEZ+O2-only ALD depositions at 230 °C and 280 °C with growth per cycle of 0.1 and 0.36 Å/cycle and (002) orientation; these distinct processes are not captured. (2) Numerous required numeric fields are null, violating the schema and completeness: processParameters.pressure, processParameters.filmThickness, nucleationPeriod, flowRates (precursor/co-reactant/purgingGas), materialProperties.uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, roughness.value, filmDensity.value, deviceProperties metrics, and otherAspects.filmStability/reproducibility. (3) DosingTime and purgeTime values are wrong by 10^3: the article gives 1.65 s and 4.4 s, but the schema unit used is MilliSEC; values should be 1650 ms and 4400 ms, not 1.65 and 4.4. (4) Electrical resistivity units are incorrect: the article reports 0.53 and 14.7 Ω·cm; the extraction records 0.53 and 14.7 with unit OHM-M. Correct conversions are 0.0053 and 0.147 Ω·m. (5) plasmaPower is included as null (should be omitted or provided as a valid object if PEALD were used). (6) filmComposition.atomicRatio set to 1:1 with XRD is not traceable; the article does not report composition or atomic ratio and XRD cannot provide it. (7) Saturation is set to True without support in the text. To improve completeness: add separate structured processes for Film C and the DEZ+O2-only processes (including temperatures, co-reactants, and reported GPCs), correct dosing/purge times to ms, convert resistivities to OHM-M, remove or populate all currently null required numeric fields (or omit optional sections), omit plasmaPower, remove the unsubstantiated atomic ratio, and set required booleans to true/false rather than null.
